Hi all, for the moment we have reverted this change to how the `eq` filter works in the <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/hubl/functions#crm-objects|crm_objects>, <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/hubl/functions#crm-object|crm_object>, and <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/hubl/functions#crm-associations|crm_associations> HubL functions because of an issue we saw. I will report back once we plan to re-enable this change.
